      "type": "factual",
      "topic": "prior-art",
      "content": "Several community projects wrap Claude Code as a subprocess for remote access (claude-code-server, claude-code-webui, CloudeCode, 247-claude-code-remote). None intercept the permission system remotely via hooks — they either pre-approve tools or relay stdin/stdout. Our HTTP hook approach would be novel.",
      "source": {
